Winterbloom was an [[Entwives|Entwife]] who appeared alongside the [[Entwives|Ent]] [[Snaggleroot]]. She was invented for ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Rings of Power]]'' television series by [[Amazon Studios]], where she appeared in the second season of the show. She is voiced by Olivia Williams.
